      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle. just like, one small glass of wine to take the edge off? i feel like a little bit shouldn't be an issue and it might actually help the diazepam kick in faster so i don't lay there awake for hours. isn't a tiny bit okay?",
