      "content": "i just feel like you're being super strict. i've heard people say that a little bit of alcohol actually helps the meds work smoother. if i just have a few sips, it won't be like i'm passing out or anything, right? i just really need to sleep and i'm worried if i don't take something to help the diazepam work, i'll be up all night again. isn't there some way to make it safe?",
